The eastern face of Tale, dominated by 2 volcanoes and home of the ["FireDrake"]s.  Oria is the home of the LawfulBad ["FireDrake"], ["Brownie"]s, and the YellowShard of HexForce.

 * neighbors ["Borea"], ["Austra"], ["Dysia"] and ["Euia"]
 * allied with ["Dysia"]
 * opposed to ["Euia"] and particularly ["Occia"]
 * ethically ["LawfulBad"]
 * politically libertarian
 * home of the YellowShard of HexForce
